!docs/.gitignore
!docs/.vitepress
!docs/images
!docs/index.md
!docs/public
.DS_Store
.idea
docs/.vitepress/cache
docs/.vitepress/dist
node_modules
.claude

# Files mirrored into every theme by bin/shell_cmd.sh at build time.
# Source of truth lives in docs/cms/ (and docs/farmart/ for ecommerce extras).
# Do not commit the mirrors — sync regenerates them on `npm run docs:build`.
docs/*/installation-command-line.md
docs/*/installation-requirements.md
docs/*/installation-using-docker.md
docs/*/installation-web-interface.md
docs/*/ssl.md
docs/*/cronjob.md
docs/*/upgrade.md
docs/*/usage-analytics.md
docs/*/usage-email.md
docs/*/usage-media-bunnycdn.md
docs/*/usage-media-s3.md
docs/*/usage-media-wasabi.md
docs/*/usage-multi-language.md
docs/*/plugin-translation.md
docs/*/usage-newsletter.md
docs/*/api.md
docs/*/plugin-backup.md
docs/*/usage-social-login.md
docs/*/usage-custom-css-js.md
docs/*/license.md
docs/*/theme-rename.md
docs/*/invoice-template.md
docs/*/usage-currencies.md
docs/*/usage-location.md
docs/*/images/backup-list.png
docs/*/images/social-login-settings.png

# Re-include canonical sources:
# - docs/cms/** is the source for the 21 standard files + 2 images.
# - docs/farmart/{invoice-template,usage-currencies,usage-location}.md is
#   the source for the ecommerce extras only (farmart itself receives the
#   cms files via sync, so those mirrored copies stay ignored above).
!docs/cms/installation-command-line.md
!docs/cms/installation-requirements.md
